<TEXT>
<P>
Off the Wall: Ken and Bob, the morning duo on KABC-AM (790), will take it to 
the wall when they host live broadcasts from the Berlin Wall starting today and 
continuing through Friday. Station officials said that Ken and Bob will be 
conversing with Berlin residents from all walks of life, observing their 
lifestyles and exploring their emotions about the past and the future. The show 
will cover everything from politics and economics to freedom and fashion. The 
program will air daily from 5 to 9 a.m. GREG BRAXTON 
</P>
