PATENTS; COMPUTER INDUSTRY; SUITS; SETTLEMENTS; ALPHA MICROSYSTEMS; GENERAL 
AUTOMATION INC; HITACHI LTD; MOTOROLA INC; SEMICONDUCTORS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
